  <summary>5/22/2003--Introduced.
National Amusement Park Ride Safety Act of 2003 - Amends the Consumer Product Safety Act to extend the definition of consumer product to include amusement rides permanently fixed to a site (thereby granting the Consumer Product Safety Commission jurisdiction over such rides).</summary>
